beer_brewer_name: Hair of the Dog Brewing Company
review_blob: Magnificent. Privileged to enjoy from bottle at HOTD on 11/2213. Think of a higher carbonated cherry Adam ftw with subtle peaches. This is my new favorite beer, and I?m an IRS lover. Fruity floaties seemed to have settled down, at least in my bottle.
